item.content:
&lt;p&gt;The files provided in this repository are intended to provide a starting point for developing a responsive multi-language Web-Site with the &lt;a href=&quot;http://get-simple.info/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;GetSimple CMS&lt;/a&gt;. The files require the use of several plugins for GetSimple and include a new theme, InnovationGrid. This theme is based on the default GetSimple &lt;a href=&quot;http://get-simple.info/extend/theme/innovation-theme/104/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Innovation theme&lt;/a&gt;, but is responsive, using CSS3 techniques.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This repository contains template, style and component files required for the InnovationGrid theme as well as a number of page files that describe the site and provide necessary functions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Users have to install the &lt;a href=&quot;http://get-simple.info/download/&quot;&gt;GetSimple CMS&lt;/a&gt; as well as the plugins listed in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/Alan-A/GetSimple-I18N-InnovationGrid/blob/master/README.md&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;README.md&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; file before the Web-Site will function fully.&lt;/p&gt;
